<h1>Perfumer Earnest Beaux</h1>
A noble <strong>perfumer </strong>and the nose behind the popular <strong>Chanel no.5 perfume</strong><br>

<h1>Image of Earnest Beaux</h1>
<figure>
 <img src= "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f9/Ernest_Beaux.jpg" alt=   width="200px" height="200px">
